Titolo: NFL 2K2

Anno: 2001

Descrizione: NFL 2K2 is a video game released in 2001 for Dreamcast by Sega, and developed by Visual Concepts. It is the last game for the Sega Dreamcast in the series after being discontinued before Sega shifted to a third party publisher. Due to that, it was released later for PlayStation 2 and Xbox. It is the first Xbox game published by Sega. It is also the last game in the NFL 2K series to feature Randy Moss as a cover athlete.
The game along with the rest of the 2K titles on the Dreamcast have had their online components revived and are completely playable online.